content: Edit: I bought the app so I won't have to see any ads in it. I cannot get a refund through Google. I guess I can count it as a loss :( Why do you need to know my location? Will I get better prices if I live in the capital city? Really disappointed with your app. How can I get a refund?
replyContent: I understand and share your concern. The 3rd part app creation platform vehemently insists on requesting permissions 'in case advertisements are put in'. None of your data will ever be used by us. For refunds, see: https://partnerdash.google.com/apps/chatbot/chat?p=refundchat. Tip: permissions are also listed in the Play Store before purchase ;)
